introduction: Talyan began acting at the age of 6 when she was submitted to audition for an Upright Citizens Brigade skit. She didn't get the part but the actress was so taken with her that she sent her to see her commercial agent. Talyan was signed right away by Reign Kids Agency and a few months later had booked her first national commercial for Dial Nutriskin.Not long after through a sequence of events, Mary Sanders of In Momentum Management took her on as a client and she switched from a commercial agent to an agency where she would be represented across the board.Talyan loves acting, singing, and dancing. She frequents Disneyland and her favorite subject in school is Science.
